source.name: Sorted Alphabetically by Lawmakers Invited
source.description: This table shows events held by lobbyists and special interest groups for state lawmakers during the 2011 General Assembly.  These events were culled from state ethics office filings and were compiled into a spreadsheet by Capital News Service's David Saleh Rauf.  Data should be credited to Capital News Service, University of Maryland Philip Merrill College of Journalism.
